snippet.textDisplay:
Y is there a comparison being made between two artists. Everyone knows Gurdas Maan Sabh is a legend and the levels cannot be matched or compared at all. 
But at least appreciate the effort that is being made by Sukhmani & Hari, and presenting the beautiful original song in a different genre. I support them with all my heart. I am an artist too and i know being creative towards something is hard, even if presenting something old in a new way.
